oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: The Eddy Arnold Show - #033
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: The Eddy Arnold Show #33, produced and transcribed in Nashville, TN. by Brown Radio Productions. Featuring Eddy Arnold and the Tennessee Plowboys, the Willis Brothers, Roy Wiggins, and host Jud Collins. Opening theme music, 'Cattle Call'; closing theme music, 'Boil Them Cabbage Down'.
